    <item>
      <title>韩国旋风式戒严令震动市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/south-korean-stocks-tumble-won-drops-as-martial-law-declared</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈出人意料地决定在韩国实行40多年来首次戒严 — — 随后又迅速改变政策 — — 导致该国对外交易资产大幅下跌，令全球市场措手不及，一度导致美国国债收益率下降，因为交易员们寻求避风港来规避潜在的不稳定因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/south-korean-stocks-tumble-won-drops-as-martial-law-declared</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 15:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
